{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "萧十一郎重伤垂危，赵无极趁黑暗欲补刀。沈璧君在暴雨中赶到，以夺命金针逼退敌人，抱着萧十一郎逃入荒山洞穴。连城璧在雨中现身，欲劝沈璧君回去，却被沈璧君斥为伪君子后离去。司徒中平试图以连城璧的秘密要挟，被连城璧一剑刺死。沈璧君与萧十一郎在洞穴中互相依靠，萧十一郎分析敌人必会分散追击，设计以逸待劳。屠啸天率先找到，被萧十一郎和沈璧君用金针计策击杀。萧十一郎布置陷阱等待赵无极，利用沈璧君的头发做机关引诱敌人。就在两人准备迎敌时，一个神秘人突然出现，冷笑着识破了他们的计谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我迟早还是要你死在我手上！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们杀了他！……是谁杀了他？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚！滚开！全都滚开！无论谁敢再走近一步，我就叫他后悔终生！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "闪开！你有多大的胆子，敢拦住我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵虎归山，萧十一郎这一走，日后我们只怕就难免要一个个死在他手上了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "你为何不来拦住她？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "你莫忘了，沈璧君毕竟是连城璧的妻子！她若受了伤，谁承当得起？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "但你若是连城璧，现在还会认她做妻子么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，我们现在再追也不迟，反正她也走不远的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，追！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该走哪条路？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你……你一直在跟着我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "但你并没有来拦住我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "只因我明白你的心意……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你明白么？真的明白？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "若不是你，他不会落得如此地步，你怎么能不救他？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我们回去吧，无论他受的伤多么重，我都会好好照顾他的，绝不会让任何人再伤他毫发。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你……你相信他不是坏人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你说的话，我几时怀疑过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "但他们方才要来杀他时，你并没有拦阻，你明知他们要来杀他，却连一句话也没有说。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "璧君……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你若真的相信我，现在就该让我走，否则以后我永远也不要见你，因为你也和别人一样，是个伪君子！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "连公子的涵养，果然非人能及，佩服佩服。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "在下若和连公子易地相处，萧十一郎今日就再也休想逃走了，也正因如此，所以在下最多也不过只是个保镖的，连公子却是名满天下，人人佩服的大侠，日后迟早必将领袖武林。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "你究竟想说什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我只是说，连公子方才若杀了他，虽只不过是举手之劳而已，但怕被人知道连公子也会乘人之危，岂非于侠名有损？连夫人更难免伤心，如今连公子虽未杀他，他反正也是活不长的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "方才赵无极他们也已追了过来，连夫人虽未瞧见，连公子却自然不会瞧不见，现在他们既已追去，夜雨荒山，以连夫人之力，又还能逃得多远？既然已有人杀他，连公子又何必自己出手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "这些话，你自然不会对别人说的，是么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "连公子也知道在下一向守口如瓶，何况，在下此时正有求于连公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "你若非有求于我，也不会故意在我面前说这些话了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "连公子果然是目光如炬，其实在下所求之事，在连公子也只不过是举手之劳而已。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "江湖中人人都知道司徒中平‘稳如泰山’，依我看，却未必。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "在下也正和连公子一样，本就是别人无法看透的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "你看我是个会被人要挟的人么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "其实我也知道，你如此做，也是情非得已，只因你要求我的事，平时我是绝不会答应的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "司徒中平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "连公子已知道我要求的是什么事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_zhong_ping",
      "text": "若要人不知，除非己莫为。你们的事，有几件是我不知道的？但你们只知我涵养很深，却未想到我有时也会反脸无情的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实每个人都有两种面目，有善的一面，也要有恶的一面，否则他非但无法做大事，简直连活都活不下去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有人能真‘稳如泰山’的，也许只有死人……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是我……你刚刚睡着了？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你不该来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "为……为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你知道……我不愿意连累你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "若不是我，你怎会这样子？本就是我连累了你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "没有你，他们一样会找到我，没有你，我一样能活下去，你明白吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好，你走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我不走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这次无论你说什么，我都不会走了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "好在那些人已走了，我们总算已逃了出来，等到天一亮，我就可以送你回去，那时我……我再走也不迟。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你根本不会说谎，何必说谎呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我……说谎？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "那些人无论哪一个，都绝不会放过我的，我明白得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他们为什么一定要你死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "因为我若死了，他们就可以活得更安全，更有面子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是不是只有你才知道他们曾做过些见不得人的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "其实，你用不着告诉我，我现在也已看清这些自命侠义之辈的真面目了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他们说的，跟他们做的，完全是两回事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "所以他们为了要杀我，必定不惜用出各种手段。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "的确是这样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "所以，你还是走的好，你不必陪我死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我不走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我知道赵无极他们必定是做过许多亏心事，但厉刚呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你觉得厉刚真是个见色不乱的真君子，是不是？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "别人都这样说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我却只能这么说，在男人面前，他也许是个君子，但遇着单身的美丽女子，他身上恐怕就只剩下头发还像个君子了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "天好像已有些亮了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你真的不肯一个人走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好，那么我们一齐走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "等雨停再走不好么？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我知道你讨厌这场雨，但我却很感激。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "感激？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "就因为这场雨冲乱了我们的足迹，所以他们直到现在还没有找着我们，也就因为这场雨，所以我们才有机会逃走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "机会？什么机会？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这场雨倒真帮了他们不少忙，非但冲走了他们的足迹，连他们的味道都冲掉了，我们就算带着猎犬，只怕也追不到他们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "海灵子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们还是逃不了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这种路连我们都走不快，何况沈璧君？何况她还带着个重伤的人。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们这位连夫人的功夫，大家自然都清楚得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但至少我们现在就不知道该往哪条路上追？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "分开来追！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "text": "也好，我和海道长一道，厉兄……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "厉刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一个人走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人的掌力虽强，轻功也不弱，脑袋却不怎么样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "你是说他选错了路？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，沈璧君和萧十一郎绝不会从这条路上逃的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "海灵子",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "怎见得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "text": "因为这条路比较好走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人在逃命时，反而不会选好走的一条路的，总认为若向难走的一条路逃，别人也就很难找到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "不错，每个人都难免有这种毛病，我只奇怪，厉刚也是老江湖了，怎会想不到？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有件事，我也始终觉得奇怪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "哪件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "厉刚人称君子，不知也做了些什么见不得人的事，被萧十一郎发觉，所以才非要将萧十一郎杀死不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "他坚持要一个人走，只怕也是生怕萧十一郎在我们面前揭穿他的秘密吧。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "只要他们分开来追，我们就有机会将他们一个个杀死！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你若猜错了呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我们至少总有机会赌一赌的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们往哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "哪里都不去，就等在这里！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "就等在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "逃，我们是逃不了的，所以只有等在这里，引他们来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是……可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这样做，虽然很冒险，但至少是在以逸待劳，因为我们现在的气力已有限，已不能再浪费了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我现在只是在猜想，第一个找到我们的是谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你猜会是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "屠啸天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你为什么猜是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他的江湖经验最丰富，轻功也不比别人差。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "第一个抓到鸡的，一定是条老狐狸。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他若来了，我该怎么样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "老狐狸都难免会有种毛病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "什么毛病？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "疑心病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "所以我们就要对准他这毛病下手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "一点也不错，我们只要……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "连夫人，你怎会在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 705,
      "line_end": 707
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "你怎么到现在才来？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 709,
      "line_end": 711
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "连夫人难道在等我么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 713,
      "line_end": 713
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "我迷了路，正在等着人来送我回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 715,
      "line_end": 715
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "那位萧十一郎呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 717,
      "line_end": 717
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "他已死了，你们本就该知道他是活不长的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 719,
      "line_end": 721
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他受的伤确实很重，但若是有名医救治，还是很快就会复原的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 723,
      "line_end": 725
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "却不知他的尸身在哪里，也许还未真的断气呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 727,
      "line_end": 729
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "我跑了半夜，实在一点力气也没有了，只得将他的尸身抛下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 731,
      "line_end": 733
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "抛在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 735,
      "line_end": 735
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "黑夜之中，也不知究竟抛在哪里了，慢慢找，也许还可以找着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 737,
      "line_end": 739
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "一定可以找着的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 741,
      "line_end": 741
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "姓萧的，事已至此，你躲在里面又有什么用？还是老老实实的出来吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 745
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "得罪了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 751,
      "line_end": 751
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 755,
      "line_end": 755
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "也没什么，只不过想请连夫人先走一步，带我到山洞里去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 757,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "姓萧的，你听着，连夫人已在我手里，你若敢玩什么花样，我就叫你们连死都不得好死……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 763,
      "line_end": 763
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你这恶贼……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 777,
      "line_end": 777
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "不错，我是恶贼，你却是笨贼，你以为我在洞里，我偏在外面。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 779,
      "line_end": 781
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你……你用的是什么恶毒的暗器？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 783,
      "line_end": 783
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "只不过是沈家的金针，自然是有毒的那种。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 785,
      "line_end": 785
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你没事么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 793,
      "line_end": 793
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我只怕自己会先倒下来，我若先倒下，他也许就能再多支持一会儿，先将我杀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 795,
      "line_end": 797
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "想不到你用金针的手法，并不在我之下。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 799,
      "line_end": 801
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "一个人到了生死关头，无论做什么都会比平时做得好些的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 803,
      "line_end": 805
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好老狐狸的疑心病都很重，否则哪有鸡的活路？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 809,
      "line_end": 811
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我将他拖到洞里去好不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 813,
      "line_end": 813
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不好，他还有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 815,
      "line_end": 815
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "有用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 817,
      "line_end": 817
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "第二个来的，一定是赵无极。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 819,
      "line_end": 819
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "赵无极的为人，不但聪明，而且狡猾。聪明人大多有种毛病，就是自作聪明，狡猾的人大多胆小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 825,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你准备怎么样对付他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 831,
      "line_end": 831
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我靴筒里有把小刀，你拿出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 833,
      "line_end": 833
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你什么都不讲究，用的刀却很讲究。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 837,
      "line_end": 839
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我喜欢刀。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 841,
      "line_end": 841
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我喜欢它，并不是因为它能杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 843,
      "line_end": 843
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 845,
      "line_end": 845
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好的刀，本身就是完美的，就好像无瑕的璧玉一样，你只要将它拿在手里，心里就会觉得很满足。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 847,
      "line_end": 849
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但‘匹夫无罪，怀璧其罪’，好刀常常都会替人找来许多麻烦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 851,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我自己惹的麻烦已够多了，有没有好刀都一样。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 855,
      "line_end": 855
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你要这把刀干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 859,
      "line_end": 859
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你回过头去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 861,
      "line_end": 861
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我不必回头，无论你做什么事，我知道都是对的，何必回头？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 863,
      "line_end": 865
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这么样一来，赵无极就会认为我是面对面杀死屠啸天的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 869,
      "line_end": 871
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 873,
      "line_end": 873
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "对面有两排树，你瞧见了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 875
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "赵无极认为你杀了屠啸天，一定不敢过来，一定会退到那两排树中去，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 877,
      "line_end": 879
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不错，你不但已学会很多，而且学得很快。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 881,
      "line_end": 881
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但他退过去后又怎样呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 883,
      "line_end": 883
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你将左面一排树，选较柔韧的树枝，弯曲下来，用……用你的头发系在地面的石头或者树根上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 885,
      "line_end": 887
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你能做得到吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 889,
      "line_end": 889
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我一定能做到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 891
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你还要我做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 897,
      "line_end": 897
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "右面第三棵树，枝叶最浓密，你就躲到那棵树上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 899,
      "line_end": 901
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 903,
      "line_end": 903
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "然后你就等着，等赵无极进入树丛，牵动头发，左面的树枝一下子就会突然弹起，赵无极必定会大吃一惊，以为左面还有埋伏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 905,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他一定就会往右面闪避退却。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 909
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不错，那时你就在树上用金针招呼他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 911,
      "line_end": 911
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我明白了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 913,
      "line_end": 913
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "但你一定要把握机会，要看准他身法的变化已穷，旧力已竭，新力未生的那一瞬间出手，叫他避无可避，退无可退！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 915,
      "line_end": 917
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你放心，沈家的金针，毕竟不是用来绣花的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 919,
      "line_end": 919
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这就叫安排香饵钓金鳌，不怕他来，只怕他不来！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 921,
      "line_end": 923
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！果然是妙计！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 925,
      "line_end": 925
    }
  ],
